### 获取安装状态
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/setup/state
Accept: application/json

### 获取可用数据库驱动列表
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/setup/drivers
Accept: application/json

### 测试 SQLite 连接（raw 模式）
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/setup/test-connection
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "driverCode": "SQLite",
  "mode": "raw",
  "connectionString": "Data Source=atlas.db"
}

### 测试 SQLite 连接（visual 模式）
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/setup/test-connection
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "driverCode": "SQLite",
  "mode": "visual",
  "visualConfig": {
    "database": "atlas.db"
  }
}

### 执行完整初始化（SQLite）
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/setup/initialize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "database": {
    "driverCode": "SQLite",
    "mode": "raw",
    "connectionString": "Data Source=atlas.db"
  },
  "admin": {
    "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "P@ssw0rd!"
  }
}
